## 📁 Project Structure

```text
Ironhold-Chess/
│
├── index.html
├── README.md
└── LICENSE
```

The current game is intentionally self-contained in a single HTML file.

That file contains:

* The user interface
* Styling
* SVG artwork
* Chess engine
* AI
* Animation system
* Audio system
* Game state management

---

## 🚀 Run Locally

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/adithyanhp/Ironhold-Chess.git
```

Enter the project directory:

```bash
cd Ironhold-Chess
```

Open `index.html` in a modern web browser.

No package installation is required.

No build process is required.

No backend server is required.

---

## 🌐 Browser Support

Ironhold Chess is designed for modern browsers that support:

* ES6 JavaScript
* SVG
* CSS animations
* Web Audio API

Recommended browsers include:

* Google Chrome
* Microsoft Edge
* Mozilla Firefox
* Safari

---

## 🪟 Install as an App

Ironhold Chess can be run in its own window using the browser's install functionality.

On Windows 11:

1. Open Ironhold Chess in a supported browser.
2. Open the browser menu.
3. Choose the option to install the site as an app.

This allows the game to run in its own application-style window.

