---

## 🎯 Vision

Ironhold Chess is built around a simple idea:

> **What if a chess capture felt like a battle?**

The project combines the strategic depth of chess with the visual language of a battlefield.

The goal is not to replace chess with a different game.

The goal is to make every move feel more alive.

